data.description: Great city views from this 13th floor unit! Dual balconies, new laminate flooring, freshly painted and upgraded kitchen, like new appliances, ceramic flooring, ceramic backsplash. You will like unit location at the end of the hall for extra privacy. Reserved garage parking space and storage unit. Condo fee includes all utilities and building amenities, inground outdoor pool, gym, laundry room is free of charge, secured building with 24 hours front desk attendant. Right across street metro stop and public bus services. Walk to shops, restaurants downtown Rockville. Really a privileged location to live.
